
🩺 GlucoseGuard-PK

 🇵🇰 Diabetes Risk Prediction for Pakistan

GlucoseGuard-PK is a machine learning web application that predicts whether a person is at risk of diabetes based on health indicators.

The project was developed using the CDC BRFSS health dataset and multiple machine learning algorithms. The best-performing model was deployed using Streamlit to provide an interactive prediction interface.


🚀 Features

- Predicts diabetes risk instantly
- Interactive Streamlit web application
- Machine Learning model trained using health indicators
- SHAP explainability for model interpretation
- Clean and user-friendly interface


