⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:

bash
git clone https://github.com/amnaaashraf/glucoseguard-pk.git


Go inside the project:

```bash
cd glucoseguard-pk
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the application:

```bash
streamlit run app/app.py
```

 📈 Model Output

The application predicts whether a patient is:

- Non-Diabetic
- At Risk of Diabetes

along with the prediction probability.



